00:00:14.540 --> 00:00:18.290
I lead the user experience
team for Google accessibility.

00:00:18.290 --> 00:00:21.050
And with me, I
have Andrea Wong--

00:00:21.050 --> 00:00:23.750
she's a researcher
on accessibility;

00:00:23.750 --> 00:00:27.590
Catherine Idylle, who is a
designer on accessibility;

00:00:27.590 --> 00:00:31.220
